name: Nangahar Province
description:
Rendering produced using ASTGTM2 data at coordinates N34E070. Roughly centered in the rendering is Jalalabad. This tile was originally downloaded because it contained the Achin region where on April 13th, 2017, the US military dropped the "Mother of all Bombs" in an attempt to destroy an underground network of caves used by ISIS.
